Package: ZamCovid
Type: Package
Title: SIR Model for the Zambian COVID-19 epidemic
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Pablo",
           family = "Perez-Guzman",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "p.perez-guzman@imperial.ac.uk"))
Description: Mechanistic models of transmission of the SARS-Cov-2 (COVID-19)
    virus in Zambia. Implemented as stochastic compartmental models in odin and
    dust. Uses mcstate to perfom Bayesian evidence synthesis from
    seroprevalence and deaths data.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/pabloperguz/zam_covid
BugReports: https://github.com/pabloperguz/zam_covid/issues
